### 1. Basic Router Health Check
GET https://universal-tenant-router.netlify.app/health
HTTP 200
[Asserts]
jsonpath "$.status" == "ok"

### 2. Database Connection Check
GET https://universal-tenant-router.netlify.app/health/db
HTTP 200
[Asserts]
jsonpath "$.database" == "connected"

### 3. Read-Only Endpoint or Standard Login Check (Idempotent)
POST https://universal-tenant-router.netlify.app/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ci-test-runner@example.com",
  "password": "secretpassword"
}

HTTP 200
[Asserts]
jsonpath "$.token" exists

